org.modelio.api.ui.form

Class AbstractFieldFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.modelio.api.ui.form.AbstractFieldFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFieldFactory

    public abstract class AbstractFieldFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements IFieldFactory
    Base implementation of IFieldFactory.

    Subclass it and implement IFieldFactory.createFields(FormToolkit, Composite, ModelElement, FormFieldPage) by using createXxxx() methods implemented here.
